review_blob: Excellent Beer. Enjoyable to drink at least once a week and not get bored. Available in growlers. (Moon shine size bottles that equal a six pack and are refilled at the bar and stay fresh for about 24 hours. Too bad its not bottled in six and twelve packs that stay in the fridge for a few more days.
Good head, excellent colour, Nice sharp taste that lingured in my mouth. Still has a nice after taste that is present even after an hour of the last sip.
